los insumos con la producción. Este modelo debe incluir al menos una ecuación que represente la proporcionalidad entre los insumos y la producción.</h5>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item mbr-flex\" mbr-if=\"steps > 5\" mbr-class=\"{'last': steps == 6}\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\">\n                        <span class=\"step-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">6</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-box\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText || showCardsubTitle\">\n                        <h4 class=\"icon-subtitle card-title mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".icon-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardsubTitle\"><b>2021</b></h4>\n\n                        <h4 class=\"icon-title card-title mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".icon-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>CCTV Cameras</b></h4>\n                        <h5 class=\"icon-text mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".icon-text\" mbr-if=\"showCardText\"><b>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet,\n                                consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus cursus, lacus at fringilla lacinia, leo leo\n                                eleifend tortor, quis sollicitudin mauris ipsum a elit. Duis eget tincidunt dui, non\n                                auctor mauris.</b></h5>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item mbr-flex\" mbr-if=\"steps > 6\" mbr-class=\"{'last': steps == 7}\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-box\">\n                        <span class=\"step-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">7</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-box\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardText || showCardsubTitle\">\n                        <h4 class=\"icon-subtitle card-title mbr-blac