          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features05 trustm5\" group=\"Features\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Number\" name=\"showNumber\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icon\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#30262b\" name=\"icon\" condition=\"showIcon\" selected>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" value=\"#e0e7ff\" name=\"card\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/trustm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/trustm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"items-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <p class=\"item-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\" data-app-selector=\".item-number\"><b>1</b>\n                                </p>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-video-play mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <b>ASSESS YOUR NEEDS</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/live/h1l7LdnunWg?si=tcjZuPqufoULNyCK\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">“Cómo implementar el SG-SST de forma fácil y práctica en la pyme” (YouTube)</a>\n<br>Te mostrará paso a paso cómo estructurar un sistema de SST en una pequeña o mediana empresa.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n                        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                            <div class=\"card-box\">\n                                <p class=\"item-number mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showNumber\" data-app-selector=\".item-number\"><b>2</b>\n                                </p>\n                                <div class=\"icon-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                                    <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-video-play mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                                </div>\n                                <h4 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .icon-wrapper\">\n                                    <b>GATHER INFORMATION</b>\n                                </h4>\n                                <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".item-text\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/MVpBPv46Kv4?si=07wsUc-N4GNcGsDd\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">“Seguridad y Salud en el Trabajo” (YouTube)</a>\n<br>Explica de forma clara qué es el SG-SST, sus beneficios y cómo aplicarlo en tu entorno laboral.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
